 = zh-hans| title = 新疆喀什警方发现5枚炸弹，其中之一爆炸| url = http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/jyxw-05262014170637.html| publisher = 自由亚洲电台| date = 2014-05-26| deadurl = no| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140527231338/http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/jyxw-05262014170637.html| archivedate = 2014-05-27| accessdate = 2014-05-27}}</ref>乌鲁木齐[[快速公交|快速公交]]禁止乘客携带液体和打火机乘车。<ref>{{cite news| language = zh-hans| title = 乌鲁木齐公交安检升级 禁带液体和打火机乘快速公交| url = http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/0528/c1001-25073776.html| publisher = 人民网| date = 2014-05-28| deadurl = no| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529141928/http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/0528/c1001-25073776.html| archivedate = 2014-05-29| accessdate = 2014-05-31}}</ref>

