l =https://web.archive.org/web/20140529194215/http://www.nanzao.com/sc/china/28379/huan-shi-bao-kong-bao-dao-she-tie-biao-qian-xin-jiang-bao-ren-pi-ping-xin-zhi-hu-xi-jin |archivedate =2014-05-29 |accessdate =2014-05-29 }}</ref>新疆[[伊犁|伊犁]]州人民政府办公厅党组成员、副主任巴图尔·杜瓦买提对暴恐事件态度暧昧被立案调查。<ref>{{cite news |language =zh-hans |title =新疆一官员存在对暴恐事件态度暧昧等问题被立案调查 |url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/legal/2014-05/27/c_126553634.htm |publisher =新华网 |date =2014-05-27 |deadurl =no |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140530150253/http://news.xinhuanet.com/legal/2014-05/27/c_126553634.htm |archivedate =2014-05-30 |accessdate =2014-05-31 }}</ref>因持续不断的暴恐事件造成新疆维吾尔自治区旅游游客与去年同期相比下降了40%左右，新疆划拨专项资金，为每位到新疆的游客提供500元人民币奖励。<ref>{{cite news |language = zh-hans |title = 新疆维吾尔自治区旅游局局长:暴恐事件无法阻碍旅游发展 |url = http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2014/05/27/7551s4556872.htm |publisher = CRI国际在线 |date = 2014-05-27 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140531051620/http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2014/05/27/7551s4556872.htm |archivedate = 2014-05-31 |accessdate = 2014-05-31 }}</ref>随后，新疆旅游宣传推广中心范分良介绍，“新疆为每位赴疆游客奖500元”确实存在，但活动在是在2014年1月至4月期间展开，已结束。<ref>{{cite news |language = zh-hans |title = 新疆旅游局：“为每位赴疆游客奖500元”系误读 |url = http://society.people.com.cn/n/2014/0529/c229589-25081615.html |publisher = 人民网 |date = 2014-05-29 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140531124718/http://society.people.com.cn/n/2014/0529/c229589-25081615.html |archivedate = 2014-05-31 |accessdate = 2014-05-31 }}</ref>

